WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:01:57.039
Subtitles and audio translation will begin later. Please wait for the official start of the video.

00:01:57.040 --> 00:02:01.204
Well, good evening, family. Thank you for joining us again today.

00:02:01.205 --> 00:02:08.922
We're excited to be here. We have a lot to talk about and pray about tonight. First off, I want to tell you a cool testimony.

00:02:08.923 --> 00:02:17.679
This testimony was a shock and awe to me, but of course we all know that Jesus is wonderful.

00:02:17.680 --> 00:02:31.137
Several weeks ago, the Lord instructed me to go over to this gentleman's house, and He said, "I want you to go over and I want you to pray for him because the arteries of his heart are clogged and he doesn't know it.

00:02:31.138 --> 00:02:47.156
There's a blockage."And He said, "I want you to go over and lay hands on him because in the natural, his heart is about ready to have a heart attack."I had a vision where the Lord showed me his wife was a widow.

00:02:47.157 --> 00:02:55.426
She was alone and they're not that old. I mean, they're not elder elders, but they're not old.

00:02:55.427 --> 00:02:59.712
I don't even think they're old enough to be my mom and my dad, do you? No.

00:02:59.713 --> 00:03:12.312
So, the Lord warned me about this man and He said, "I want you to go over there and pray for him."Well, when I was there, I said, "I'm not trying to scare you, but this is what the Lord is telling me.

00:03:12.313 --> 00:03:22.106
So, I want to pray for you. Is it okay if I pray for you?"Because I'm not just going to lay hands on anyone who doesn't want me to pray for them. But he asked me when I walked in.

00:03:22.107 --> 00:03:44.238
He said, "Brandon, I felt inside that maybe you could pray for something that I'm having a need of."And I said, "Well, okay."He said, "I have two hernias in my body that are pretty severe, and I'm scheduled to have surgery."I believe it was a couple of weeks out.

00:03:44.239 --> 00:04:05.070
And he said, "But I'm believing that if you pray for me and we agree together, that I'll be healed."Because certain people know that the Lord has put healing in my hands. I don't make it a widely known thing.

00:04:05.071 --> 00:04:21.749
I know the Lord told me when Ralph Wilkerson touched my hands and he said, "These hands are going to have fire in them."He touched my hands, he touched the palm of each one of my hands, and he said, "I'm putting a double portion of the anointing on my life on you."This is Ralph Wilkerson at Melodyland Christian Center.

00:04:21.750 --> 00:04:38.604
Back in 2001 he did this. Ever since then, my hands get hot with fire, but I never know when it's going to happen when I'm praying for somebody.

00:04:38.605 --> 00:04:53.119
Sometimes it's like touching a cold stove. In this situation, he said, "Will you please pray for me for these hernias?"And I was like, "Okay, well, I came here to pray for your heart.

00:04:53.120 --> 00:05:04.719
The Lord told me about your heart."And he goes, "Wow."I could see he was kind of concerned about it on his face, but I didn't want to make a big deal out of it or let him know what I saw in the spirit, which was that this man was about to die.

00:05:04.720 --> 00:05:18.279
And so I prayed for him. I put his hand on his groin area and I put my hand on top because it's awkward—I'm not going to touch a man like that.

00:05:18.280 --> 00:05:31.507
I prayed for him a prayer of faith and I laid hands on him. I didn't hear anything, just like it was with the man with the lungs who got healed and got two brand-new lungs.

00:05:31.508 --> 00:05:36.478
The doctor told him he was going to die and he needed a lung transplant.

00:05:36.479 --> 00:05:52.011
Anybody knows that story? I've told it before. Well, a couple of weeks go by and my wife got a text from his wife.

00:05:52.012 --> 00:06:04.079
She said, "Good morning. I have to share a prayer report with you. My husband has been going to doctors for over two years.

00:06:04.080 --> 00:06:11.425
He was diagnosed with double hernias and they have been waiting on him to have surgery.

00:06:11.426 --> 00:06:20.015
He's been putting it off and had so much stress about having surgery for quite some time.

00:06:20.016 --> 00:06:29.245
He went again to a new doctor last month, right after he asked Brandon to pray for him.

00:06:29.246 --> 00:06:41.439
He had several tests and ultrasounds again. The results came back yesterday. It's a total answer to prayer.

00:06:41.440 --> 00:07:02.719
I had to share below a picture of the report findings."The power of God touched him; the hernias are completely gone, both of them. And the doctor said, "You don't have to have surgery.

00:07:02.720 --> 00:07:13.444
All the hernia and all the evidence of the hernia, even through the ultrasound, is completely gone."And he had had this and he was suffering. It hurt; he said it was very uncomfortable.

00:07:13.445 --> 00:07:32.757
Of course, he had two major hernias and they had scheduled him six weeks out from having the surgery because he was like, "I'm just going to go ahead and do it."So the power of God touched him and I was just giving all the glory to the Lord for it.

00:07:32.758 --> 00:07:45.261
Isn't Jesus wonderful? I went over there to give him the word about the heart and Jesus touches the hernias that were bothering him.

00:07:45.262 --> 00:07:55.679
I thought, we are in the last days. I talked to my friend Billy Burke today. I love that man.

00:07:55.680 --> 00:08:03.433
I know for a fact what the Lord has shown me about his ministry and what's going to happen in the days ahead with great signs and wonders, even more than what he already walks in.

00:08:03.434 --> 00:08:20.349
But I know whenever the Lord told me "cross-pollination,"when you start talking to people that walk underneath an anointing and you sow into their ministry and you believe by faith, it's a covenant.

00:08:20.350 --> 00:08:29.994
You start giving and you start believing. I already know what the Lord has told me, that I'll walk in healings, but I don't know when it's going to come on like that full-time.

00:08:29.995 --> 00:08:54.520
All I know is the Lord said, "Brandon, I'm going to use you one day with this and I'll use Diana with you."And even Billy has given Diana words about how she'll pray for babies that are dead in the womb—where the mother has gotten a bad report of a baby that has been diagnosed as not alive anymore—and the power of God, by laying hands on the mother, is going to raise that baby from the dead.

00:08:54.521 --> 00:08:59.219
I truly believe that in the resurrection power of the Lord Jesus.

00:08:59.220 --> 00:09:09.728
I was so excited for him that he doesn't have to have surgery now and that he got such a great report.

00:09:09.729 --> 00:09:18.189
I don't want things like that to ever just bypass you; I want to always stay in awe of Jesus for what He's done in these last days.

00:09:18.190 --> 00:09:31.083
Oh, Father, thank you. And like He said, "Brandon, never take a miracle for granted. Never look at it as insignificant when I touch somebody.

00:09:31.084 --> 00:09:37.302
For when there are so many miracles that are about to take place, don't become familiar with my glory.

00:09:37.303 --> 00:09:45.834
Don't become familiar with what I'm doing in ministry."I know beyond a shadow of a doubt. I've seen dogs raised from the dead.

00:09:45.835 --> 00:09:54.376
I've seen people carrying an oxygen tank behind them, completely grayed out on the verge of death.

00:09:54.377 --> 00:09:58.028
I've laid hands on them and God gave them two brand-new lungs. They came back.

00:09:58.029 --> 00:10:02.398
The doctor said, "We're taking you off the donor's list,"completely healed by the power of God.

00:10:02.399 --> 00:10:13.728
They were delivered after they sprayed Roundup on the ground for 40-some years for the city and breathing in all those chemicals every single day destroyed their lungs.

00:10:13.729 --> 00:10:20.668
He had an oxygen tank and ran up to me saying, "I've been healed."I just came back to tell you.

00:10:20.669 --> 00:10:28.527
I didn't know who he was because he wasn't ashy-looking. His skin had pigment. He looked great and I'll never forget it.

00:10:28.528 --> 00:10:52.060
I thought, "Wow, Jesus."As I went back into some of the things the Lord has shown us about healings and things that are about to take place, I thought of "can these bones live?"and the dead in Christ rising first.

00:10:52.061 --> 00:10:57.665
He said, "Randy, you don't realize that all that which remains will be caught up.

00:10:57.666 --> 00:11:17.681
You don't know there's a little bit of a gap there."There's a lot of people that talk about creation—that whenever God made the earth, there's a gap between the verses, between "let"and how the dinosaurs ruled in that time frame.

00:11:17.682 --> 00:11:30.163
I think Rick Renner teaches it. I'll butcher it; I am not a theological Greek person, but I know Rick Renner does that and he is very gifted at it.

00:11:30.164 --> 00:11:39.039
He talks about creation and the gap. Dr. Carl Baugh, I believe, is who it was. I remember hearing him one day talking about the gap.

00:11:39.040 --> 00:11:45.614
But I was just trying to encourage you all that God's moving, shaking, and doing things.

00:11:45.615 --> 00:11:50.569
I have such an anticipation for these last days and what God's about to do.

00:11:50.570 --> 00:11:56.159
Billy was saying he was believing God to have a meeting here at the Mabee Center.

00:11:56.160 --> 00:12:00.380
Who would be interested? Let us know in the comments down below when you're on that live.

00:12:00.381 --> 00:12:09.163
Can you tell us if we had a meeting at ORU and we rented out the Mabee Center, would you come?

00:12:09.164 --> 00:12:17.805
I'm just curious before I take money and invest in it. Would you come? Would you like to have a healing meeting?

00:12:17.806 --> 00:12:27.362
I'll be there and I'll have to have security, but Billy Burke's going to do the services.

00:12:27.363 --> 00:12:32.255
I'll be sitting in the congregation supporting him, praying, and enjoying the service.

00:12:32.256 --> 00:12:41.034
I won't be speaking, but I believe in my friend and the anointing on his life; I believe in the gift.

00:12:41.034 --> 00:12:51.922
It touches me. After Megan went to Eufaula, she no longer has plays in her periods; Jesus is touching her.

00:12:51.923 --> 00:13:04.605
That's why I get so many little nuggets from people. I always try to be a friend to authentic people that really truly love the Lord.

00:13:04.606 --> 00:13:16.392
I just wanted to throw that out there. I didn't know if there's anybody who would be interested in having a meeting, coming to Tulsa, and doing the Mabee Center at ORU.

00:13:16.393 --> 00:13:24.765
It holds 3,500 people. I wonder if we could fill it. I just truly believe we could.

00:13:24.766 --> 00:13:32.398
I believe there's going to be something. The Lord said, "It'll be a dome of glory there.

00:13:32.399 --> 00:13:40.471
It's going to be a time of glory over you."I thought, "What if this is the beginning of it?"because Billy brought it up to me today.

00:13:40.472 --> 00:13:52.398
He said, "It's been on my heart, Brandon. I've been praying about it."He asked, "What do you feel?"I thought I'll pray about it, too. Let's do this.

00:13:52.399 --> 00:14:04.471
So, if you're interested and you put it in the comments, if you think, "Hey, I'd like to come to Tulsa and have a healing revival,"let's do it.

00:14:04.472 --> 00:14:08.903
I thought what a time that would be to have it. He said, "I don't want to do it at a church or hotel.

00:14:08.904 --> 00:14:14.439
Maybe we could do it there at ORU."So, we'll have to look into it and see if ORU would let us do it.

00:14:14.440 --> 00:14:22.700
I don't think we would fill up the Mabee Center there yet at 10,000, but I believe we could really fill up the 3,500.

00:14:22.701 --> 00:14:31.470
So, maybe I might need to stretch my faith that big. I just know that people are hungry and maybe you would want to be a part of it.

00:14:31.471 --> 00:14:35.627
I'll bring that to you, and if you're interested, let us know.

00:14:35.628 --> 00:14:41.570
Also, I just want to say from the last video, I apologize for my attitude.

00:14:41.571 --> 00:14:50.433
I apologize for how I said the word and told everybody they could go to heck and the attitude that I had.

00:14:50.434 --> 00:14:57.039
The Lord really got onto me after it was over and said, "You don't represent me like that.

00:14:57.040 --> 00:15:04.582
You don't talk that way."I'm ashamed of that. I just want to tell you I apologize for how I handled that.

00:15:04.583 --> 00:15:09.682
I get under pressure, and it's like I told Billy. He said, "Brandon, it's okay.

00:15:09.683 --> 00:15:13.000
You were just ankle-deep that day."We go from glory to glory.

00:15:13.001 --> 00:15:21.352
We go from ankle-deep to knee-deep to waist-deep to over the head.

00:15:21.353 --> 00:15:29.271
Just in that day, in that moment, my toes weren't even wet. I said, "You're being generous.

00:15:29.272 --> 00:15:39.792
I wasn't ankle-deep. My toes weren't even wet, brother. I was all in the flesh."But I just wanted to ask you all to forgive me for being an idiot.

00:15:39.793 --> 00:15:45.089
I appreciate it. We're all a work in progress and Brandon still has issues.

00:15:45.090 --> 00:15:55.529
I work through things; I have things I get over with anger, yelling, and getting mad at stupid people on the road. You have to just calm yourself down and get in the Word more.

00:15:55.530 --> 00:16:14.394
It's like he said, when you're going through life and the devil's tempting you to get in the flesh, the only way he gets you is if you're empty. Let your full fight for you.

00:16:14.394 --> 00:16:28.159
The only way you're able to resist the devil is your word level and your spirit level—being filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit, being word and spirit.

00:16:28.160 --> 00:16:36.434
There's too much "word of faith"where it's out of kilter and you don't add the Spirit to it where you flow with the Holy Ghost and have the Word.

00:16:36.435 --> 00:16:44.238
You can't just be totally Word and you can't just be totally Holy Spirit; you get flaky. You have to have a balance.

00:16:44.239 --> 00:17:13.796
He instructed me: "As people that have temptations with anger, getting upset, or acting out..."I get all kinds of messages: "Brandon, I'm dealing with addictions, drugs, alcohol, pornography, or lust."It's a sign of being ankle-deep.

00:17:13.797 --> 00:17:31.227
We must stay filled in these last days. That was what the Lord was showing me even more today: "Brandon, you get low on the Word."The less you are filled with and controlled by the Holy Ghost, the more you don't stay full.

00:17:31.228 --> 00:17:41.855
Let your full fight for you. The more you stay full, the more you can submit yourself unto God, resist the devil, and he will flee.

00:17:41.856 --> 00:17:51.927
I just want to encourage everybody. The problem is if we don't know the truth, the truth won't set us free.

00:17:51.928 --> 00:18:04.239
The more you know the truth of God's Word, the truth will set you free. The entrance of His Word brings forth light.

00:18:04.240 --> 00:18:14.596
The light is illuminating; it brings forth that Holy Ghost and fire as you're reading the pages of this beautiful book.

00:18:14.597 --> 00:18:25.605
It becomes life and rhema knowledge over your mind the more you meditate on the Word of God. It will change you from the inside out.

00:18:25.606 --> 00:18:33.651
The fuller you get of God's Word, when you submit yourself unto God and you resist the devil, he will flee from you.

00:18:33.652 --> 00:18:38.345
But you have to learn that you have to get in that Word and yield yourself.

00:18:38.346 --> 00:18:44.309
How much do you need the Holy Spirit today? I need you. I depend on you.

00:18:44.310 --> 00:18:49.832
The moment you put your foot out of the bed onto the carpet: "I need you.

00:18:49.832 --> 00:18:59.913
Fill me."You have to stay in that place of being filled. In these last days, you don't understand where we're headed.

00:18:59.914 --> 00:19:10.478
You don't understand the "shaking to awaken"that we're about to experience in this generation. The Lord said very sobering days are coming.

00:19:10.479 --> 00:19:27.119
But if you understand Psalm 91 and Psalm 23 and you understand how to be filled with the Holy Ghost to the overflow—not just being weird, but surrendering all to him.

00:19:27.120 --> 00:19:44.953
Surrender all to him today and say, "I need you."The moment you recognize that you need him, you realize our dependency on him. I can't do this without you. I'm sold out to Jesus.

00:19:44.954 --> 00:20:04.373
When you talk to elders and people who have lived ministry for a long time—years and years, more than I've been alive—and you talk to people that are still going, you learn from people that have fruit, that are still going strong in their almost 80s.

00:20:04.374 --> 00:20:13.306
You go, "Hey, there's something more to what you're saying. I've got to learn this."Stay full. Stay full.

00:20:13.307 --> 00:20:17.804
There are so many times that you say, "Well, I'm dealing with this. I'm dealing with that.

00:20:17.805 --> 00:20:26.079
I can't get over this."Call those things that be not as though they were.

00:20:26.080 --> 00:20:35.195
But the only way you do that is knowing who you are in Christ and by sitting at His feet and basking in His presence on a day-to-day basis.

00:20:35.196 --> 00:20:55.442
I told you Jesus said, "It is written, Satan, man shall not live by bread, but every word that proceedeth out of the mouth of the Father."When the devil tried to tempt Him, "Turn this stone into bread, Jesus,"but Jesus dealt with flesh just like every single one of us.

00:20:55.443 --> 00:21:09.468
Jesus was man; He was God created in flesh. But He dealt with temptations, heartache, and pain. Billy said people don't want to talk about John 7.

00:21:09.469 --> 00:21:20.714
I remember what the verse was—he talked about how Jesus had to flee because the religious people were trying to kill Him.

00:21:20.715 --> 00:21:29.585
He had to flee for a season, and he said a lot of people won't want to talk about that, but the Bible clearly says that Jesus had to go away because it wasn't His time yet.

00:21:29.586 --> 00:21:36.319
They tried to kill Him before His time. He talks about it because I was talking about having to hire security and all this stuff.

00:21:36.320 --> 00:21:42.327
I said, "Is that fear?"And he's like, "Brandon, no, I think it's wisdom."So, I'm hiring full-time security.

00:21:42.328 --> 00:21:50.954
I've got people that are—what was it? Is it this one? No, not the Tested Son.

00:21:50.955 --> 00:22:03.439
Okay, that's when Jesus was tested in the wilderness. I don't remember; I'll have to ask him again. I'm sorry, I believe it's John 7.

00:22:03.440 --> 00:22:09.652
But he talked about how Jesus had to leave certain areas because they were trying to kill Him, and He's the Son of God.

00:22:09.653 --> 00:22:14.736
It was interesting because it was in the Bible, and he said there are certain verses that have always challenged me.

00:22:14.737 --> 00:22:22.865
I think about what he says, and I go, "Yeah."What I'm trying to tell you is that Jesus had stuff He was working through just like we do.

00:22:22.866 --> 00:22:28.880
As perfect and awesome as He was, Jesus had to deal with flesh just like us.

00:22:28.881 --> 00:22:31.639
He had to say, "Hey, listen, Satan. You're not going to tempt me.

00:22:31.640 --> 00:22:35.036
You get out of here."And the only way—He didn't pray the devil away.

00:22:35.037 --> 00:22:55.916
He didn't sit there and go, "Well, I'm going to pray to God to handle this,"or "I've got to go into a 30-day fast praying in tongues."He spoke to him: "It is written."It was the word that came out of Jesus's mouth that got rid of the devil—the Holy Ghost in Him flowing the word of God.

00:22:55.917 --> 00:23:00.558
He submitted himself unto God, he resisted the devil, and he fled.

00:23:00.559 --> 00:23:08.558
Everything that Jesus did, we can do. As He is, so are we in this world.

00:23:08.559 --> 00:23:17.839
We are made in His image. He was tempted on everything and every level, but He was sinless.

00:23:17.840 --> 00:23:27.592
If He can go sinless staying full of the word of God, that means He wouldn't tell us we could do something that was impossible.

00:23:27.593 --> 00:23:37.720
He did it. How did He do it? He stayed full. He stayed full. Acting out in anger?

00:23:37.721 --> 00:23:41.368
He didn't have problems with this. Why? Because He stayed full.

00:23:41.369 --> 00:23:54.351
The moment the tempter came to try to destroy—and He was in the wilderness for that time and having a weak moment—He was full enough to say, "It is written, Satan.

00:23:54.352 --> 00:24:10.211
Get out of here."Every single time, He was victorious. And how He was able to remain that purified life was staying full with the Spirit of God and the Word.

00:24:10.212 --> 00:24:16.556
He kept himself submitted, going vertical continually. He didn't go horizontal; he stayed vertical.

00:24:16.557 --> 00:24:21.098
He was always saying, "I don't do anything unless I'm instructed to by the Father.

00:24:21.099 --> 00:24:26.287
I only say what the Father tells me to say."He was always staying vertical.

00:24:26.288 --> 00:24:35.234
He was staying full. That's where we have to be. If Jesus did it, I'm going to mirror my life after Him.

00:24:35.235 --> 00:24:42.123
Yesterday, my toes weren't even wet. I wasn't even halfway full. I had a rough day.

00:24:42.124 --> 00:24:49.732
I talked to my mom, had family stuff I was dealing with, and by the time I came on live, I was already empty.

00:24:49.733 --> 00:24:54.234
I should not have talked about certain things yesterday. I shouldn't have done certain things, but I did.

00:24:54.235 --> 00:24:58.643
By the time I got on here, you embarrass yourself by not staying full.

00:24:58.644 --> 00:25:05.687
So, I'm trying to tell y'all: stay full. Stay full. Keep yourself underneath those wings.

00:25:05.688 --> 00:25:10.879
That's the only way you're going to make it in these last days.

00:25:10.880 --> 00:25:13.944
It's like listening to that still, small voice on the inside.

00:25:13.945 --> 00:25:19.646
He won't yell; He'll guide us. For those that are led by the Spirit of God are the sons of God.

00:25:19.647 --> 00:25:28.529
I'm going to keep myself in that place in the cleft of the rock, keeping myself in His hand, listening to Him, and saying, "Father, I need you.

00:25:28.530 --> 00:25:36.234
I'm staying vertical. We attract to deflect."I want to encourage y'all today that Jesus is still healing people.

00:25:36.235 --> 00:25:46.762
I've got the testimony. Maybe I'll have him on one day and he can testify to you himself, tell you how Jesus healed him of two hernias.

00:25:46.763 --> 00:25:50.959
It's amazing to hear people that I know and that we lay hands on.

00:25:50.960 --> 00:25:58.631
Was it Brandon that healed him? No, it was Jesus. He can use any one of us.

00:25:58.632 --> 00:26:09.905
But it was a moment that He said, "Hey, I want to flow through you today."I'm so grateful that He did. Isn't that awesome? So stay full. It's time to stay full.

00:26:09.906 --> 00:26:21.439
To the ones that have reached out saying they want to be my security—and you've said you'll move your family here from all over—we've had several emails today from people who want to be security for me.

00:26:21.440 --> 00:26:29.953
You are ex-military, Special Forces, all kinds of stuff. I appreciate the offer.

00:26:29.954 --> 00:26:36.073
We'll look over it. My wife and I will pray about it, and if I have a peace, I'll reach out to you.

00:26:36.074 --> 00:26:51.706
I want to know your credentials, what kind of background you have—military, law enforcement, whatever you may have—and how you know Jesus. I'm not going to have an unbeliever around me.

00:26:51.707 --> 00:27:12.282
If you know the Holy Ghost, are baptized in the Holy Ghost, and you are on fire and can hear Him and are discerning—if there's some danger around and you feel in your spirit, "Hey, there's something here, Brandon"—I believe it. I take no counsel from the ungodly in any area of my life.

00:27:12.283 --> 00:27:28.247
You could be the best trained military operative in the whole world, but if you don't hear the voice of the Lord in these last days and you can't tell me, "I feel the Holy Ghost inside of me telling me there's danger,"then I won't even look your direction.

00:27:28.248 --> 00:27:35.994
I need to verify it. I'll hear by the Holy Ghost who is hearing the Lord in these last days. I have a budget.

00:27:35.995 --> 00:27:54.675
I'm believing God for the money to do all this, setting it aside for security to be with me to do these meetings and the things I feel the Lord has called me to do to make sure my family is safe.

00:27:54.676 --> 00:27:59.539
So, if you have a military background and you're Holy Ghost filled, maybe we can talk.

00:27:59.540 --> 00:28:05.839
If not, I'm sorry. I'm not interested. I have to have people who hear the voice of the Lord.

00:28:05.840 --> 00:28:14.229
I believe Charlie Kirk would still be here if he would have had better security and people that were baptized in the Holy Ghost around him.

00:28:14.230 --> 00:28:21.439
